title: 3000 Items Design Bundle
description:
This amazing bundle has been brought back to Mighty Deals, by popular demand!
If you're a Web designer or developer, well, you may want to sit down for this one. This Mighty Deal may be the mightiest one we've ever offered and when you're finished ordering, you're totally going to feel like a kid in a candy store!
You know that designer's toolbox you've got tucked away somewhere on your hard drive? Well, time to get a new one. A bigger one. Way bigger. That's because this Mighty Deal is a Mega Design Bundle full of over 2.5GB of graphical elements. 
To be exact, this deal consists of a bundle of bundles. Get 22 design-based collections and sets all wrapped up in one neat little package. All that's missing is the bow!
